house of dust is a 2013 supernatural thriller film directed by a.d. calvo .   the movie had its world premiere on may 5 , 2013 and focuses on a group of college students that become possessed by the ghosts of former mental patients .   filming took place in willimantic , connecticut and mansfield , connecticut at the mansfield training school and hospital , university of connecticut , and eastern connecticut state university during the summer of 2011 .